description.eng:
Standard: BEP20
Blockchain: BSC
Decimals: 18 Total
SeAPT is a next-generation meme coin built on the BSC network.
The ownership of SeAPT coins lies with the SeAPT users, and naturally, the power belongs to them as well.
Although Binance advised burning 200 trillion tokens, we decided to burn 300 trillion instead.
Following the spirit of SeAPT, we’ll use these funds to help many people and promote SeAPT worldwide.
As various exchanges keep asking for SeAPT coins, we’ll allocate some to them and use the rest for marketing.
